---
title: Honey Halloumi & Cheesy Chipotle Slaw Bowl with Charred Corn & Garlic Aioli
description: Let’s fill the bowl to the brim with salty golden slices of halloumi, pan-fried sweetcorn and a chipotle sauce slaw with a hit of lime to add a dash of zest and tang. Tonight will be bursting with both colour and flavour.

*We’ve replaced the lemon in this recipe with lime due to local ingredient availability. It may be a little different to what’s pictured, but just as delicious!*
